    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      <h4>New</h4>
        <h3><img src="https://heroespatchnotes.com/images/hero/blaze.png" alt="Blaze" height="60" width="60" /> Blaze</h3>
      <h4>Battleground</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><p>Regen Globes: healing reduced 23%, mana regen reduced 10%</p>
</li>
        <li><p>Gate, Fort, and Keep damage increased 33% vs "Minions, Mercenaries, Monsters, and Heroes"; Keep health increased 6%</p>
</li>
        <li><p>Mercenary updates: Hellbats and Warhead Junction boss have health and early-game scaling reduced, late-game scaling increased; Knight camp spell armor now equal between defender and laner</p>
</li>
        <li><p>Towers of Doom: Altar respawn increased 20 seconds</p>
</li>
        <li><p>Battlefield of Eternity: first immortal spawn and swap events are now fixed; first spawn will be "Heaven South, Hell North", first swap will be "Heaven East, Hell West"</p>
</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Heroes Affected</h4>
