  <entry>
    <title type="text">2017-12-12 Patch Notes v 2.29.3</title>
    <published>2017-12-12T17:30:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-12-12T17:30:00.000Z</updated>
    <id>https://heroespatchnotes.com/patch/2017-12-12-patch-notes.html</id>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/patch/2017-12-12-patch-notes.html"/>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      <h4>New</h4>
        <h3><img src="https://heroespatchnotes.com/images/hero/hanzo.png" alt="Hanzo" height="60" width="60" /> Hanzo</h3>
      <h4>Gameplay</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><p>Camera height: "In-game Camera height has been significantly increased in order to provide more visibility of the battlefield"</p>
</li>
        <li><p><a href="http://us.battle.net/heroes/en/blog/21273594">Stealth reworked</a>: stealth heroes now display outlines, become completely invisible when immobile for 1.5 seconds</p>
</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Play Mode</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><p><a href="http://us.battle.net/heroes/en/blog/21179036">Performance-based matchmaking</a>: "takes individual player performance into account when determining MMR gains and losses"; Five days later, <a href="https://eu.battle.net/forums/en/heroes/topic/17617601839#post-3">Performance based matchmaking was disabled</a> due to unrelated "issue[s] affecting placement matchmaking ratings"</p>
</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Battleground</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><p><a href="http://us.battle.net/heroes/en/blog/21295033">Early game and laning changes</a>: Ammo removed from towers, Forts and Keeps reveal Stealth, regen globes "switch from allied to neutral after 3 seconds", most Battleground objective timers have been altered, Mercenaries updated with special abilities</p>
</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Heroes Affected</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/abathur.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Abathur</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/muradin.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Muradin</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/nova.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Nova</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/samuro.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Samuro</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/sgthammer.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Sgt. Hammer</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/thelostvikings.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">The Lost Vikings</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/tyrande.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Tyrande</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/valeera.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Valeera</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/valla.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Valla</a>, 
          <a href="https://heroespatchnotes.com/hero/zeratul.html#patch2017-12-12" target="_blank">Zeratul</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
